snippet.title: SNES Longplay [035] Super Turrican (US)
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: T-0815

Longplay includes: all extra lifes / all diamonds / all hidden areas

Level 1-1: 01:41 --- 1-2: 05:26 --- 1-3: 09:45
Level 2-1: 16:46 --- 2-2: 20:08 --- 2-3: 24:08
Level 3-1: 31:38 --- 3-2: 33:32 --- 3-3: 35:52
Level 4-1: 37:52 --- 4-2: 44:11 --- 4-3: 45:57

I know we already have a Super Turrican longplay (made by Retroplay) on our website. This longplay is made solid, but shows almost none of the numerous secrets. 

So I decided to make a new longplay. It contains all the hidden areas and the best path to all extra lifes and diamonds (and there are tons).

It really took quite a while, until everything was the way I've imagined. But now I am quite happy with it. I hope you like it. Have fun !

"Another day, another try, but remember: SHOOT OR DIE!"

Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
